<HL>
   Marketing &amp; Media:
   Ex-Inquirer Editor Roberts
   Accepts University Tenure
</HL>
<DATE>
09/06/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   WNEWS KRI
</CO>
<IN>
